
WIKID is a website managment system 
based on CodeIgniter PHP Framework and CKEditor javascript online editor.

-> /licenses/ folder contains a copy of every licenses and copyrights involved in this application
-> /system/ folder contains CI system files
-> /application/ folder contains CKEditor files (in 3rdparty subfolder) and all Wikid files
-> /index.php file is the CI front controller
-> /wikid.config.php file contains specific config for a WKD website


How to setup a new website from a given Wikid (what should I change)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
-> edit /wikid.config.php
-> edit /wikid.config.js
-> set RewriteBase in /.htaccess



