Main changes in CodeIgniter (watch out on update)
-------------------------------------------------
-> /application/config/config.php (require wikid.config.php)
-> /application/config/database.php (require wikid.config.php)
-> /application/config/autoload.php
-> /.htaccess (mode rewrite)


